movies.title: French Immersion
movies.synopsis: In this comedy from Kevin Tierney, four strangers from different parts of North America meet in Quebec to attend Isidore-du-Coeur-de-JA (C)sus, an French language program for adults, where everyone seems to end up acting like teenagers. ~ Cammila Albertson, Rovi

movies.title: French Affairs
movies.synopsis: When Astrid, a professional therapist, starts having an affair with her patient Celine's husband, it puts a strain on an already difficult relationship with her son, David.

movies.title: French Kiss
movies.synopsis: A case of mistaken identity leads to a troublesome moral dilemma for a man who's fallen hopelessly in love. The first time Fred met Julie, she mistook him for an old classmate. Hopelessly smitten, he simply played along. But as the romance turns serious, Fred becomes paralyzed with fear at the thought that his deception will be revealed, and Julie will leave him forever. ~ Jason Buchanan, Rovi

movies.title: French Blood (Un Francais)
movies.synopsis: This drama covers two decades in the life of a French white supremacist, as the political party he's involved with grows in power. Based on true events. Directed by Diasteme.
